1
00:00:10,940 --> 00:00:14,020
ظآزLove crosses every cycle
of life and deathظآز

2
00:00:14,300 --> 00:00:17,580
ظآزSo let me fall with youظآز

3
00:00:17,580 --> 00:00:20,420
ظآزAll the noise of the mortal worldظآز

4
00:00:20,420 --> 00:00:24,060
ظآزIs nothing compared to her eyesظآز

5
00:00:24,060 --> 00:00:27,180
ظآزWhoever said love itself is sinظآز

6
00:00:27,380 --> 00:00:31,020
ظآزWhen a heartbeat turns into
wind and moonlightظآز

7
00:00:31,020 --> 00:00:34,180
ظآزPainting a banquet
of endless spring bloomsظآز

8
00:00:34,620 --> 00:00:35,700
ظآزHow beautifulظآز

9
00:00:35,700 --> 00:00:38,860
=Blooms for Her=

10
00:00:38,900 --> 00:00:41,820
=Episode 24=

11
00:01:07,760 --> 00:01:08,560
This strike

12
00:01:09,200 --> 00:01:10,239
is for my parents!

13
00:01:17,760 --> 00:01:20,319
(And for all of us
whom you once saw as ants.)

14
00:01:37,319 --> 00:01:38,120
Jinghe,

15
00:01:39,359 --> 00:01:40,879
I finally have my revenge.

16
00:01:43,640 --> 00:01:45,680
But they're never coming back.

17
00:01:56,480 --> 00:01:58,200
Wherever you go from now on,

18
00:01:58,920 --> 00:02:00,159
you still have me.

19
00:02:14,319 --> 00:02:15,120
Father,

20
00:02:15,800 --> 00:02:16,599
Mother,

21
00:02:17,080 --> 00:02:19,120
I've avenged you at last.

22
00:02:20,280 --> 00:02:22,000
Please rest in peace,

23
00:02:22,719 --> 00:02:24,080
both of you.

24
00:02:31,520 --> 00:02:32,639
Once the court stabilizes,

25
00:02:32,800 --> 00:02:34,199
I'll give up the throne

26
00:02:35,639 --> 00:02:36,759
and retire with you.

27
00:02:40,479 --> 00:02:41,400
Before that,

28
00:02:43,120 --> 00:02:44,719
will you go back to the palace with me

29
00:02:45,080 --> 00:02:46,560
as my empress for a while?

30
00:02:49,479 --> 00:02:50,280
Jinghe.

31
00:02:51,039 --> 00:02:51,759
What is it?

32
00:02:51,759 --> 00:02:53,680
Daliang has no heir yet.

33
00:02:53,960 --> 00:02:55,199
The officials will surely object.

34
00:02:55,759 --> 00:02:57,000
Can you really step away?

35
00:02:58,439 --> 00:02:59,759
I promised you.

36
00:03:00,120 --> 00:03:01,199
I'll keep my word.

37
00:03:11,460 --> 00:03:13,860
(South Gate)
(Two Months Later)

38
00:03:19,319 --> 00:03:21,560
Your Majesty,
you look so gorgeous in this dress.

39
00:03:21,919 --> 00:03:23,759
It suits you perfectly.

40
00:03:28,840 --> 00:03:30,240
This outfit

41
00:03:31,080 --> 00:03:32,360
is so ugly.

42
00:03:32,879 --> 00:03:33,919
What were you whispering,

43
00:03:33,919 --> 00:03:34,479
Your Majesty?

44
00:03:36,560 --> 00:03:37,360
Nothing.

45
00:03:37,439 --> 00:03:38,879
The court is still unstable.

46
00:03:39,000 --> 00:03:42,000
We beg you to abandon
this idea of abdication, Your Majesty.

47
00:03:42,080 --> 00:03:44,120
Please reconsider, Your Majesty.

48
00:03:44,759 --> 00:03:45,759
It's my throne.

49
00:03:46,240 --> 00:03:48,800
Do I need your permission to give it up?

50
00:03:49,439 --> 00:03:51,439
Your Majesty, if you insist on this,

51
00:03:51,479 --> 00:03:54,439
I'll hit the pillar today

52
00:03:54,759 --> 00:03:56,000
to remonstrate unto death!

53
00:03:56,199 --> 00:03:56,759
Very well.

54
00:03:56,879 --> 00:03:57,960
I'll grant your wish.

55
00:03:58,439 --> 00:03:59,039
Guards!

56
00:04:01,719 --> 00:04:03,319
You shameless woman!

57
00:04:03,439 --> 00:04:05,439
How dare you strike out
in front of His Majesty?

58
00:04:06,719 --> 00:04:07,680
You deserve it!

59
00:04:08,319 --> 00:04:09,479
When the realm was in peril,

60
00:04:09,479 --> 00:04:10,319
where were you?

61
00:04:10,560 --> 00:04:12,319
When tyranny ran rampant
in the old court,

62
00:04:12,400 --> 00:04:13,280
where were all you

63
00:04:13,280 --> 00:04:15,120
so-called loyal ministers?

64
00:04:15,520 --> 00:04:16,959
Now that peace has been restored,

65
00:04:17,399 --> 00:04:19,079
you suddenly change your tune

66
00:04:19,199 --> 00:04:20,959
and threaten His Majesty with your life?

67
00:04:21,439 --> 00:04:22,439
This is outrageous!

68
00:04:25,360 --> 00:04:26,639
Well said.

69
00:04:29,480 --> 00:04:30,319
Get out!

70
00:04:33,360 --> 00:04:34,560
If any of you

71
00:04:34,560 --> 00:04:36,319
threatens me with their life again,

72
00:04:36,800 --> 00:04:37,920
I will grant that wish too.

73
00:04:38,959 --> 00:04:40,720
And I will

74
00:04:40,720 --> 00:04:41,959
erase their entire clan.

75
00:04:42,959 --> 00:04:43,759
Yes, Your Majesty.

76
00:05:07,060 --> 00:05:09,020
ظآزMoonlight spills like quiet tidesظآز

77
00:05:09,270 --> 00:05:12,240
ظآزA celestial bird
brushes the mountain's edgeظآز

78
00:05:14,100 --> 00:05:15,580
ظآزWings of light drift through the airظآز

79
00:05:15,580 --> 00:05:19,260
ظآزLike blossoms that refuse to fadeظآز

80
00:05:20,040 --> 00:05:23,060
ظآزIt asks no right or wrongظآز

81
00:05:23,300 --> 00:05:26,060
ظآزNor fears the turning of fateظآز

82
00:05:27,180 --> 00:05:28,780
ظآزA trace of spring on the windظآز

83
00:05:28,860 --> 00:05:31,420
ظآزA whisper of a broken heartظآز

84
00:05:33,300 --> 00:05:35,380
ظآزA farewell song unfoldsظآز

85
00:05:35,660 --> 00:05:38,580
ظآزCarrying every sorrow within itظآز

86
00:05:38,980 --> 00:05:41,020
ظآزKarma weaves its endless threadظآز

87
00:05:41,140 --> 00:05:44,980
ظآزAnd I would follow you
without turning backظآز

88
00:05:45,460 --> 00:05:48,460
ظآزLife and death become
nothing sharp or finalظآز

89
00:05:48,780 --> 00:05:51,860
ظآزLove and hate are carried away
on the breezeظآز

90
00:05:52,460 --> 00:05:54,660
ظآزBefore freedom is ever reachedظآز

91
00:05:54,660 --> 00:05:57,700
ظآزOne must first dissolve into tearsظآز

92
00:05:58,300 --> 00:06:01,380
ظآزLove crosses every cycle
of life and deathظآز

93
